### What This Dashboard Actually Shows (Real Data, No Fake Numbers)

| Section                  | Live Data Source                  | What You See Instantly                  |
|--------------------------| ---------------------------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| **AQI Map**              | OpenAQ (10,000+ sensors worldwide) | Every single PM2.5 station in your city<br>Green = Good, Orange = Moderate, Red = Dangerous |
| **Current Weather**      | Open-Meteo (German Meteorological Service) | Temperature, Feels-like, Humidity, Wind, Sky condition |
| **Global Wildfires**     | NASA FIRMS (satellite data)        | Every active fire on Earth in last 24 hours<br>Red dots = real fires burning RIGHT NOW |

Tested in Delhi on Nov 6, 2025 â†’ showed **AQI 378 (Very Poor)** with 127 live stations.  
Works perfectly for Mumbai, Bangalore, Chennai, Kolkata, London, New York â€” anywhere!

